  <header>
    <h1>Marketplace Reordering (Ankorstore)</h1>
    <p>Reordering • Conversion • Cart UX</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Context</h2>
    <p>Ankorstore’s B2B marketplace saw high drop-off when merchants tried to re-order frequent items. The cart flow was cumbersome and lacked quick reorder options.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Objectives</h2>
    <p>• Build an intuitive “Reorder” feature<br>
       • Revamp cart to boost order completion<br>
       • Align the platform to retailer needs</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Process</h2>
    <p>• Strategy workshop with PMs, designers, analysts<br>
       • Interviews across FR, ES, UK (18 users)<br>
       • Prototype in Figma + Maze tests (24 users)<br>
       • Iterative design with dot-voting and RICE</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Results</h2>
    <p>• Reorder button cut order time from 17 to 5.5 minutes<br>
       • Cart redesign improved completion rate by 10%<br>
       • Retailer satisfaction rose with simplified flow</p>
  </section>

</body>
</html>          
